import React from 'react';
import {Form,Button} from 'react-bootstrap';

class newProject extends React.Component{

	render () {
		return (
			<Form>
				<Form.Group controlId="formProjectName">
					<Form.Label>项目名称</Form.Label>
					<Form.Control  placeholder="Project name" />
				</Form.Group>

				<Form.Group controlId="formGoal">
					<Form.Label>众筹金额</Form.Label>
					<Form.Control placeholder="Goal" />
				</Form.Group>
				<Form.Group controlId="formMaxInvest">
					<Form.Label>个人最大投资</Form.Label>
					<Form.Control placeholder="MaxInvest" />
				</Form.Group>
				<Form.Group controlId="formMinInvest">
					<Form.Label>个人最小投资</Form.Label>
					<Form.Control placeholder="MinInvest" />
				</Form.Group>

				<Form.Group controlId="formSymbol">
					<Form.Label>众筹代币名称</Form.Label>
					<Form.Control placeholder="Symbol" />
				</Form.Group>
				<Form.Group controlId="formName">
					<Form.Label>众筹代币详细名称</Form.Label>
					<Form.Control placeholder="name" />
				</Form.Group>
				<Form.Group controlId="formDecimal">
					<Form.Label>代币小数</Form.Label>
					<Form.Control placeholder="Decimal" />
				</Form.Group>
				<Form.Group controlId="formStartDate">
					<Form.Label>开始投票日期</Form.Label>
					<Form.Control placeholder="StartDate" />
					<Form.Text className="text-muted">不填写默认为当前时间</Form.Text>
				</Form.Group>

				<Button variant="primary" type="submit">
				Submit
				</Button>
			</Form>
		);
	}

};

export default newProject;
